data.description: Property is back on market, buyer's loss is your gain.  Welcome to country living just minutes from Ft Knox! This charming well cared for bedford stone ranch features 3 bedrooms, 1 bathroom, unfinished walkout basement, and a large detached workshop/2-car garage with plumbing and electrical, providing a comfortable and spacious country living experience. Situated on a quiet country road, this property is perfect for those seeking tranquility while still enjoying the conveniences of Ft Knox and Etown. Don't miss the chance to make this house your home! Schedule a viewing today and discover the perfect blend of peace, comfort, and convenience.
